00:00:54.310 --> 00:00:59.600
 automatically. 

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.320
 Use of the autoclave 

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:07.960
 Separate distilled water according to the size of your autoclave: 150 ml to 

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:12.030
 12 liters and 250 ml for 21 liters. 

00:01:12.030 --> 00:01:16.100
 Put water into the autoclave chamber. 

00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:21.350
 In block 54 the supply is automatic. Distribute the packages inside 

00:01:21.350 --> 00:01:27.390
 autoclave on the inner trays or on the accessory holder. 

00:01:27.390 --> 00:01:32.680
 Do not overlap packages and always load paper up. 

