00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:50.920
 heating and sterilization. 

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:54.090
 When depressurising, wait for the beep 

00:01:54.090 --> 00:01:56.260
 and open for drying. 

00:01:56.260 --> 00:02:01.330
 At the end of the cycle the green LED will flash. 

00:02:01.330 --> 00:02:06.520
 When the packages are cold, store them in the closet. 

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:11.300
 To use your Vitale Plus after it is switched on select the appropriate cycle for 

00:02:11.300 --> 00:02:13.469
 the articles you will use. 

00:02:13.469 --> 00:02:18.669
 If you have assorted materials that require different cycles, choose the option 

00:02:18.669 --> 00:02:24.169
 where the temperature is lower and the drying time is longer. 

00:02:24.169 --> 00:02:25.869
 Press the start key 

00:02:25.869 --> 00:02:28.409
 and the program is automatic. 

00:02:28.409 --> 00:02:31.669
 Drying will happen with the door closed. 

00:02:31.669 --> 00:02:36.269
 When it is finished, the end of cycle display will appear. 

00:02:36.269 --> 00:02:41.139
 Remove the packages when cold and store them in your own closet. 

00:02:41.139 --> 00:02:46.629
 To sterilize liquids use only the exclusive cycle. 

